rd/Ethics">Ethics</a></span>, <span class="hlFld-KeywordText"><a href="/keyword/Multinationals">Multinationals</a></span>, <span class="hlFld-KeywordText"><a href="/keyword/National+Accounts">National accounts</a></span>, <span class="hlFld-KeywordText"><a href="/keyword/Social+Audit">Social audit</a></span>, <span class="hlFld-KeywordText"><a href="/keyword/Social+Responsibility">Social responsibility</a></span></dd><dt>Type: </dt><dd><compound-subject-part xmlns:mml="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" content-type="label">General review</compound-subject-part></dd><dt>Publisher: </dt><dd><span class="NLM_publisher-name">MCB UP Ltd</span></dd><span class="copyRight"><dt>Copyright:</dt><dd>Â© MCB UP Limited 1996<br />Published by <span class="NLM_publisher-name">MCB UP Ltd</span><br /><license-p xmlns:mml="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"></license-p></dd></span></dl>
